1 0 0 1 50 766 Tm (Last Updated: 2026-04-01) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 752 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 738 Tm (1. Who we are) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 724 Tm (TravelNest Technologies Private Limited \("TravelNest", "we", "our", "us"\) is a travel booking) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 710 Tm (platform for flights, hotels, and holiday packages.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 696 Tm (For privacy queries, contact privacy@travelnest.in.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 682 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 668 Tm (2. Data we collect) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 654 Tm (We collect profile data \(name, email, phone, date of birth\), identity data \(passport/government) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 640 Tm (ID details where required for international travel\), booking details, payment-related metadata,) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 626 Tm (device and location signals, customer support communications, and loyalty activity.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 612 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 598 Tm (3. Why we process your data) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 584 Tm (We process personal data to create and manage accounts, complete travel bookings, process) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 570 Tm (payments/refunds, prevent fraud, provide customer support, send booking updates, and improve) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 556 Tm (service quality.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 542 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 528 Tm (4. Legal basis and consent) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 514 Tm (Where required, we rely on your consent for specific processing \(including marketing) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 500 Tm (communications\). You may withdraw consent at any time from account settings or by contacting) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 486 Tm (us.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 472 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 458 Tm (5. Sharing of data) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 444 Tm (We share relevant data with airlines, hotels, payment processors, identity verification) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 430 Tm (vendors, customer support providers, and regulators/law enforcement where required by law.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 416 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 402 Tm (6. Cross-border processing) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 388 Tm (Certain partners and cloud infrastructure providers may process data outside India. We apply) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 374 Tm (contractual and security safeguards and comply with applicable transfer restrictions.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 360 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 346 Tm (7. Data principal rights) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 332 Tm (You may request access, correction, update, and erasure of your personal data, and raise) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 318 Tm (grievances through our support channels.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 304 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 290 Tm (8. Security safeguards) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 276 Tm (We implement encryption in transit, role-based access controls, monitoring, and periodic) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 262 Tm (security reviews to protect personal data.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 248 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 234 Tm (9. Retention) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 220 Tm (We retain data for as long as necessary for booking fulfillment, fraud prevention, legal) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 206 Tm (obligations, dispute handling, and accounting requirements. Data is deleted or anonymized when) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 192 Tm (no longer necessary.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 178 Tm () Tj
